{"tid":2069351,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國再創奇蹟：北京疫情已經控制住了","createTime":"2020-06-18T10:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T11:01:49.000Z","uid":48040,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5805e33a041a7297309853b87d5ad6586836c585","tid":2069351,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"今天下午，在北京市新冠肺炎疫情防控工作新聞發布會上，中國疾控中心流行病學首席專家吳尊友明確告訴大家，北京疫情已經控制住了。<br />\n<br />\n吳尊友表示，每天新診斷報告病例不等於新感染的，對發病時間分析可知，大部分在幾天以前就出現發病症狀，從感染到發病還有一段時間，所以昨天新增的21個人都是在6月12日以前發生的感染。如果把病人發病時間在做一個曲線，高峰發生在6月13日。<br />\n<br />\n那是不是明天就沒有病人報告了？不是，還會有，這些病例都是對既往感染病例的檢測發現，不是新感染的病例，但病例數會越來越少。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bj.people.com.cn/BIG5/n2/2020/0618/c14540-34097367.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbj.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2Fn2%2F2020%2F0618%2Fc14540-34097367.html&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=86f372ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bj.people.com.cn/BIG5/n2/2020/0618/c14540-34097367.html</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_OtH-ee5lSw&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=dd89bbc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_OtH-ee5lSw</a>"},{"pid":"277d47a13f843368ed2e2eeeca537e86e27134bf","tid":2069351,"uid":162478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:15:26.000Z","msg":"問我國家哪像染病 希望林鄭上北京取經"},{"pid":"5e0fe2373413ec0e0f7ac2ae7938336f81801fd3","tid":2069351,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"cef213f4e2d900a1041c53193934641c4f5c7530","tid":2069351,"uid":73569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"全球今日都冇確診<br />\n確診病染既係尋日既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b1ab04e3f86bd39b03c48435e8d2afe1d2408b","tid":